\[\frac{1}{c_{2}}=\int_{0}^{\infty}e^{-c_{2}x}dx=\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\int_{(k-1) \alpha}^{k\alpha}e^{-c_{2}x}dx\geq\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\alpha e^{-c_{2}\alpha k}.\]

