\[\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}e^{-c_{2}\alpha k}=1+\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}e^{-c_{2}\alpha k} =1+\frac{1}{c_{2}\alpha}=(\alpha+\frac{1}{c_{2}})\alpha.\]

