\[\left|\mathbb{E}\left[\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}D^{i}(h\circ\varphi_{n-(k+1)})(\theta_{k })\left(g(\theta_{k+1},X_{k+1})-g(\theta_{k},X_{k})\right)\right]\right| \leq C.\] (18)

